  \x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}Howard began to cry.

  \x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\"And don't go turning on the weeps, either, or you'll get switched right now.\"

