  \x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}The egg began to emit creaking sounds. It seemed to move a little, and from its apex a noise of tapping came. \"It's the heat expanding it,\" said Papa.

  \x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}The tapping became louder. An irritating scratching accompanied it. The egg shook and rolled a little. \"Back up a little, everybody,\" said Papa. \"Looks like the thing was going to turn over.\"

  \x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}A grating, tearing sound came from the top of the egg, and a hunk of shell fell off at their feet. A yellow bill the size of a plowshare stuck out of the egg.

