  \x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\x{a0}\"But that doggone Mauser bullet it wanted blood, an' it hits a flat rock an' ricochets up into the crowd of onlookers an' smacks a little kid right in the temple an' drops him in his tracks.

